Caste Baseline

We conducted a survey with approx. 3612 existing respondents from the CASTE project in Bihar. The survey was conducted in April 2020 and included a number of questions on topics related to coronavirus such as, health preserving behaviour, current economic activities, policing and lockdowns, beliefs and knowledge of covid-19 and usage of social benefits.
